Integrate CRM Analytics into Salesforce with an Analytics Tab

Access your CRM Analytics home and run CRM Analytics apps from a tab within Salesforce Classic or Lightning Experience.

The CRM Analytics tab is available in new CRM Analytics-enabled orgs. In existing orgs, set up the CRM Analytics tab as you would any new tab.

The CRM Analytics tab can include features such as annotations, notifications, sharing and downloading options, links to other CRM Analytics assets, a record actions menu, and a link to CRM Analytics Studio for users but not Experience Cloud sites users.
title: Integrating CRM Analytics into Salesforce
